contra a parede.

1426
01:15:55,780 --> 01:15:58,162
Hum, eu adorei essa ideia.

1427
01:16:00,202 --> 01:16:02,354
Devia ter escolhido
a Martha Stewart,

1428
01:16:03,002 --> 01:16:06,281
